node.text:
Jillian Bell discovers the aisle where it all ends. And begins. In this episode of Home Sweet HomeGoods, Jillian goes into HomeGoods to find an amazing deal on a wedding gift and instead, finds herself a home. Permanently.
 
At HomeGoods, you never know what you’ll find. In this
series...Jillian Bell finds a home. With the help of some lovable associates she learns a little more about herself, and learns that she has a knack for interior design and a love of great prices. Hilarity ensues as customers are shopping for furniture, wall decor, mirrors, rugs, and sometimes, even for the sofa right out of her living room.
 
Starring Jillian Bell, as herself. And HomeGoods, as itself.
Directed by John Riggi.
 
Watch the full 6-episode series: https://www.instagram.com/homegoods/channel/

Did Jillian stumble into the Rom-Com aisle? In this episode of Home Sweet HomeGoods, Jillian makes new friends and decides where she wants to go from here. If anywhere?

At HomeGoods, you never know what you’ll find. In this series...Jillian Bell finds a home. With the help of some lovable associates she learns a little bit more about herself, and learns that she has a knack for interior design and a love of great prices. Hilarity ensues as customers are shopping for furniture, wall decor, mirrors, rugs, and sometimes, even for the sofa right out of her living room.

Starring Jillian Bell, as herself. And HomeGoods, as itself.
Directed by John Riggi.

Watch the full 6-episode series: https://www.instagram.com/homegoods/channel/
